      "writtenOn": "2026-02-24T15:25:46Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is quite big actually: if anyone is using this interface (e.g. multi-site) how does he know *IF* the runtime implementation of this interface will be thread-safe or not?\n\nI believe we should be stricter if we have evidence that common brokers have this limitation.\n\nI see two options:\n\n1. Just documenting it in a stricter way\n2. Documenting *and* checking it",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 37,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 39,
        "endChar": 78
      },
      "revId": "273162b6d5404474d678876c6b76ec7957d7a880",
